<U><B>Native American Facts For Kids</U></B> was written for young people in search of Blackfeet information for school or home-schooling reports. 
We encourage students and teachers to visit our main <A href="http://www.native-languages.org/blackfoot.htm">Blackfoot</a> website
for in-depth information
about the tribe, but here are our answers to the questions we are most com<img src="singledot.png">monly asked by children, with 
Blackfoot pictures and links we believe are suitable for all ages. Photographs are the property of the sources
we have credited.</font><BR><BR>

